### Send Email
POST {{host}}/coms/send/email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

{
  "toEmails": ["user@example.com"],
  "emailTemplate": "auth/pin-inicio-sesion",
  "data": {
    "date": "2024-07-10 14:30",
    "pin": 654321
  }
}

###

### Send Email — with fromEmail override and documentIds
POST {{host}}/coms/send/email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

{
  "fromEmail": "no-reply@hospitalsm.org",
  "fromName": "Hospital SM",
  "toEmails": ["user1@example.com", "user2@example.com"],
  "emailTemplate": "adm/auto-admision",
  "data": {
    "patientName": "Juan Perez",
    "documentId": "123456789",
    "date": "2024-07-15",
    "code": 123456
  },
  "documents": [
    {
      "bucket": "hsm-docs",
      "files": [
        {
          "folderName": "generated",
          "fileInfo": { "fileId": "32e4e180-b307-42c8-8240-096c749a9188" }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

###

### List Email Batches
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/batches
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### List Email Batches — filtered by status and date range
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/batches?overallStatus=SENT&fromDate=2024-01-01&toDate=2024-12-31&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### Get Email Batch by ID
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/batches/[batchId]
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### Resend Email Batch
POST {{host}}/coms/emails/batches/[batchId]/resend
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### List Email Recipients
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/recipients
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### List Email Recipients — filtered by batchId and status
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/recipients?batchId=[batchId]&status=FAILED&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### Get Email Recipient by ID
GET {{host}}/coms/emails/recipients/[recipientId]
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### Resend Email Recipient
POST {{host}}/coms/emails/recipients/[recipientId]/resend
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

###

### Send SMS (stub — not yet implemented)
POST {{host}}/coms/send/sms
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{at_token}}

